cmd to run test:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Go to directory '/design/ca/dv'
2. Use command :   xrun -f ca_tb.args 
   This will help run the preset test 'ca_basic_test_c' from the script file 'ca_tb.args'
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

